'''ᱠᱟᱨᱛᱤᱠ ᱛᱤᱣᱟᱨᱤ''' (ᱡᱟᱱᱟᱢ ᱒᱒ ᱱᱚᱣᱟᱢᱵᱚᱨ ᱑᱙᱙᱐<!-- DO NOT CHANGE! This has been verified by a high-quality reliable source-->), ᱫᱚ ᱦᱚᱲ ᱠᱚ ᱴᱷᱮᱱ '''ᱠᱟᱨᱛᱤᱠ ᱟᱨᱭᱟᱱ''' ᱢᱮᱱᱛᱮ ᱵᱟᱰᱟᱭ ᱠᱟᱱᱟᱭ ᱾ ᱱᱩᱭ ᱫᱚ ᱢᱤᱫ ᱵᱚᱞᱤᱣᱩᱰ ᱟᱠᱴᱚᱨ ᱠᱟᱱᱟᱭ ᱾ ᱵᱟᱭᱳᱴᱮᱠᱱᱳᱞᱳᱡᱤ(biotechnology) ᱨᱮ ᱤᱝᱡᱤᱱᱤᱭᱚᱨᱤᱝ ᱯᱟᱲᱦᱟᱜ ᱚᱠᱛᱚ ᱨᱮ ᱱᱩᱭ ᱫᱚ ᱢᱚᱰᱮᱞᱤᱝ ᱮᱦᱚᱵ ᱞᱮᱫᱟᱭ ᱟᱨ ᱟᱠᱴᱚᱨ ᱵᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱨᱮᱭᱟᱜ ᱡᱚᱥ ᱫᱚᱦᱚ ᱞᱮᱫ-ᱟᱭ ᱾ ᱯᱮ ᱥᱮᱨᱢᱟ ᱚᱱᱟ ᱫᱷᱟ.ᱲ ᱨᱮ ᱠᱷᱟᱴᱟᱣ ᱠᱟᱛᱮ ᱒᱐᱑᱑ ᱥᱟ.ᱦᱤᱛ ᱨᱮ ᱠᱟᱨᱛᱤᱠ, ᱯᱩᱭᱞᱩ ᱞᱮᱠᱟᱛᱮ ''[[ᱯᱭᱟᱨ ᱠᱟ ᱯᱚᱧᱪᱱᱟᱢᱟ]]'' ᱨᱮ ᱠᱟ.ᱢᱤ ᱧᱟᱢ ᱠᱮᱫ-ᱟ ᱾ ᱱᱚᱶᱟ ᱯᱷᱤᱞᱢ ᱫᱚ [[ᱞᱚᱵᱷ ᱨᱚᱱᱡᱚᱱ]]-ᱮ ᱰᱤᱨᱮᱠᱴᱚᱨ ᱞᱮᱫ-ᱟ ᱟᱨ ᱞᱮᱰᱤ ᱟᱠᱴᱚᱨ ᱞᱮᱠᱟᱛᱮ [[ᱱᱩᱥᱨᱚᱛ ᱵᱷᱚᱨᱩᱪᱟ]] ᱢᱮᱱᱟᱭᱟ ᱾

ᱠᱟᱨᱛᱤᱠ ''[[ᱟᱠᱟᱥ ᱵᱟᱬᱤ]]'' (᱒᱐᱑᱓) ᱟᱨ ''[[ᱠᱟᱧᱪᱤ: ᱫᱤ ᱚᱱᱵᱽᱨᱮᱠᱮᱵᱚᱞ]]'' (᱒᱐᱑᱔) ᱯᱷᱤᱞᱢ ᱨᱮ ᱠᱟ.ᱢᱤ ᱠᱮᱭᱟ ᱛᱚᱵᱮ ᱱᱚᱶᱟ ᱯᱷᱤᱞᱢ ᱫᱚ ᱟᱡᱟᱜ ᱡᱤᱭᱚᱱ ᱞᱟᱦᱟ ᱥᱮᱱ ᱤᱫᱤ ᱨᱮ ᱢᱚᱸᱰ ᱢᱩᱨᱩᱱ ᱮᱱᱟᱭ ᱾ ᱚᱱᱟ ᱛᱟᱭᱚᱢ ᱱᱩᱭ ᱨᱚᱱᱡᱚᱱ ᱟᱨ ᱵᱷᱟᱨᱩᱪᱟ ᱥᱟᱶᱛᱮ ''[[ᱯᱭᱟᱨ ᱠᱟ ᱯᱚᱧᱪᱚᱱᱟᱢᱟ ᱒]]'' (᱒᱐᱑᱕) ᱟᱨ ''[[ᱥᱚᱱᱳ ᱠᱮ ᱴᱤᱴᱩ ᱠᱤ ᱥᱣᱤᱴᱤ]]'' (᱒᱐᱑᱘) ᱯᱷᱤᱞᱢ ᱨᱮ ᱠᱟ.ᱡᱤ ᱠᱮᱫᱟᱭ ᱾ ᱱᱚᱶᱟ ᱵᱟᱱᱟᱨ ᱯᱷᱤᱞᱢ ᱫᱚ ᱟᱭᱢᱟ ᱠᱟ.ᱣᱰᱤ ᱠᱚᱭ ᱦᱟᱛᱟᱣ ᱞᱮᱫᱟ ᱾  ᱚᱱᱟ ᱨᱮᱭᱟᱜ ᱥᱚᱠᱥᱮᱥ ᱛᱟᱭᱚᱢ ᱒᱐᱑᱙ ᱠᱚᱢᱮᱰᱤ ᱯᱷᱤᱞᱢ ''[[ᱞᱩᱠᱟ ᱪᱷᱩᱯᱤ]]'' ᱟᱨ ''[[ᱯᱚᱛᱤ ᱯᱚᱛᱱᱤ ᱚᱨ ᱣᱩ (᱒᱐᱑᱙ ᱨᱮᱭᱟᱜ ᱯᱷᱤᱞᱢ)|ᱯᱚᱛᱤ ᱯᱚᱛᱱᱤ ᱚᱨ ᱣᱩ]]'' ᱨᱮ ᱠᱟ.ᱢᱤ ᱧᱟᱢ ᱞᱮᱫ-ᱟᱭ ᱾

== Life and career ==

=== Early life and work (1990–2017) ===

Kartik Tiwari (later Aaryan){{efn|name=A}} was born on 22 November 1990<!-- DO NOT CHANGE! This has been verified by a high-quality reliable source--> in [[Gwalior]], [[Madhya Pradesh]].<ref name=birthday>{{cite web|last=Hegde|first=Rajul|title=A happy woman is a myth, says Pyaar Ka Punchanama's Kartik Aaryan|url=http://www.rediff.com/movies/report/a-happy-woman-is-a-myth-says-pyaar-ka-punchanamas-kartik-aryan-video/20151122.htm|publisher=[[Rediff.com]]|accessdate=13 April 2016|date=22 November 2015|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160416021249/http://www.rediff.com/movies/report/a-happy-woman-is-a-myth-says-pyaar-ka-punchanamas-kartik-aryan-video/20151122.htm|archivedate=16 April 2016}}</ref><ref name="chip">{{cite news|last=Malik|first=Ektaa|title=Kartik Aaryan: New Chip of the Old Block|url=https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/bollywood-kartik-aaryan-sony-titu-sweety-new-chip-of-the-old-block-5133639/|work=[[The Indian Express]]|accessdate=2 July 2018|date=12 April 2018|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180425214630/http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/bollywood-kartik-aaryan-sony-titu-sweety-new-chip-of-the-old-block-5133639/|archivedate=25 April 2018}}</ref> Both his parents are doctors; his father is a [[paediatrician]], and his mother, Mala, is a [[gynaecologist]]. He pursued an engineering degree in biotechnology from [[Navi Mumbai]]'s D Y Patil College of Engineering, while secretly harbouring ambitions for a career in film.<ref name="engineer">{{cite web|title=The engineer who became a Bollywood hero|url=http://www.rediff.com/movies/slide-show/slide-show-1-the-engineer-who-became-a-bollywood-hero/20140423.htm|publisher=Rediff.com|accessdate=23 April 2014|last=N|first=Patcy|date=7 February 2018|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140423215510/http://www.rediff.com/movies/slide-show/slide-show-1-the-engineer-who-became-a-bollywood-hero/20140423.htm|archivedate=23 April 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Rawal Kukreja|first=Monika|url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/bollywood/mother-s-day-kartik-aaryan-says-his-mom-googles-his-name-every-day-adds-his-girlfriends-on-facebook/story-d8HuZdZqZ4L3umZVmRHRjO.html|title=Mother’s Day: Kartik Aaryan says his mom googles his name every day, adds his girlfriends on Facebook|work=[[Hindustan Times]]|date=13 May 2018|accessdate=3 July 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180702233234/https://www.hindustantimes.com/bollywood/mother-s-day-kartik-aaryan-says-his-mom-googles-his-name-every-day-adds-his-girlfriends-on-facebook/story-d8HuZdZqZ4L3umZVmRHRjO.html|archive-date=2 July 2018|url-status=live}}</ref> He has said that he would skip his classes and travel for two hours to attend auditions.<ref name="dna18">{{cite news|last=Rakshit|first=Nayandeep|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/bollywood/interview-sonu-ke-titu-ki-sweety-actor-kartik-aaryan-now-people-are-calling-me-a-hot-chocolate-boy-2587229|title=Sonu Ke Titu Ki Sweety actor Kartik Aaryan: Now, people are calling me a ‘hot-chocolate boy’|work=[[Daily News and Analysis]]|date=22 February 2018|accessdate=2 July 2018|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180410062553/http://www.dnaindia.com/bollywood/interview-sonu-ke-titu-ki-sweety-actor-kartik-aaryan-now-people-are-calling-me-a-hot-chocolate-boy-2587229|archivedate=10 April 2018}}</ref><ref name="firstpost18">{{cite news|last=Srivastava|first=Abhishek|url=https://www.firstpost.com/entertainment/kartik-aaryan-says-contrary-to-popular-belief-sonu-ke-titu-ki-sweety-is-not-a-recreation-of-pyaar-ka-punchnama-4360615.html|title=Kartik Aaryan says contrary to popular belief, Sonu Ke Titu Ki Sweety is not a recreation of Pyaar Ka Punchnama|work=[[Firstpost]]|date=21 February 2018|accessdate=2 July 2018|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180312140604/http://www.firstpost.com/entertainment/kartik-aaryan-says-contrary-to-popular-belief-sonu-ke-titu-ki-sweety-is-not-a-recreation-of-pyaar-ka-punchnama-4360615.html|archivedate=12 March 2018}}</ref> Aaryan began a modelling career while in university and after three years of unsuccessfully auditioning for films, he did an acting course from the Kreating Charakters institute. He informed his parents of his desire to become an actor only after he signed his first film.<ref name="engineer" /><ref name="filmfare14">{{cite news|last=Loynmoon|first=Karishma|url=http://www.filmfare.com/interviews/i-didnt-know-how-to-kiss-5960.html|title=I didn't know how to kiss|work=[[Filmfare]]|date=24 April 2014|accessdate=27 February 2015|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141020202103/http://www.filmfare.com/interviews/i-didnt-know-how-to-kiss-5960.html|archivedate=20 October 2014}}</ref>

